data.description: Seller will pay $6,000 towards Loan interest rate/closing costs/upgrades. A Renovated 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home. 2 master rooms with attached bathrooms. Upstairs has a bedroom an office - with deck look out - it may be used as a 5th bedroom with closet or loft/family room.  Home has easy maintenance (approx. 2 year old) wood machined laminate flooring through-out. Furnace and AC compressor replaced in 2018, Gas Range in 2021, Main Well Pump in 2021 and irrigation pump in past year. This home is located just south of town in an established neighborhood. It's been mostly upgraded/renovated with: windows, doors (including hardware), flooring, light fixtures, interior and exterior mostly painted and more. A 16 X 40 foot concrete floored shop with 7 foot wide door entry (Other garage). Land has ample room for a Motor Home/RV parking by side of main Garage. Beautifully sized yard with Pear, Apricot, and Apple trees plus a tilled garden area. Quiet peaceful living with view of horse pasture from yard. Thank you.
